title: NLP - Bandler, Grinder, Erickson, John La Tourette & more
description:
NLP other good stuff.

If you have downloaded my other nlp torrents, then you have some of this material already.  I am consolidating my NLP stuff into one torrent.

I will continue uploading new material, however, I don't want to have to seed and keep up with multiple torrents.  I'm far too ADD for that. If anyone has a knows how to add new material to an existing torrent, let me know.

Anyway, here is 15 gigs of new material: Richard Bandler, John Grinder, John La Tourette, and Kenrick Cleveland.  And the old Michael Hall and NLP Colorado Institue stuff.

If videos are extremely bad (not just bad) quality or don't play, reply in the comments and I will search for a better version.

Know some NLP greats that I missed? Add to comments, and I may be able to get them.
